sequenceDiagram
  actor Analyst
  participant UI as PySide6 Workspace
  participant Loader as Telemetry Loader
  participant Analyzer as Detection Service
  participant DB as SQLite Database

  Analyst->>UI: Import JSON / NDJSON / CSV
  UI->>Loader: load_records(path)
  Loader-->>UI: Normalised records
  Analyst->>UI: Analyse telemetry
  UI->>Analyzer: analyse(records, thresholds)
  Analyzer-->>UI: AnalysisResult(summary, findings)
  UI-->>Analyst: Display summary and findings
  Analyst->>UI: Create incident from selected finding
  UI->>DB: add_incident(Incident)
  DB-->>UI: Incident ID
  UI-->>Analyst: Confirm incident created
